ezec 1.0.0
==========

NEW FEATURES
----------

* results returned as a `tbl_df` from the dplyr package.
* resulting data frame gains a column defining the sample names instead of using
  the "rownames" attribute (This was addressed in part for
  https://github.com/grunwaldlab/ezec/issues/3)

BUG FIX
----------

* samples with insufficient data no longer throw an error when running
  `EC_table` without three response levels


ezec 0.1.0
==========

initial version of ezec
